+ *
+ * - For each transaction t in the DepGraph (in some topological order);
+ *   - The size: VARINT(t.size), which cannot be 0.
+ *   - The fee: VARINT(SignedToUnsigned(t.fee)), see below for SignedToUnsigned.
+ *   - The dependencies: for every parent p of t, in order of most recently serialized to least
+ *     recently serialized:
+ *     - VARINT(diff), where diff is the number of transactions between p and the previous parent
